    %% External → Ingress
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Terminate<br/>Bearer sk-oai-* or OC token"| Gateway

    %% Gateway → Auth
    Gateway -->|"gRPC ext_authz<br/>mTLS (Istio)"| Authorino
    Authorino -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>API key validate callback"| MaaSAPI
    Authorino -->|"gRPC mTLS<br/>Token rate limit check"| Limitador

    %% Gateway → Application
    Gateway -->|"HTTPS/8443 or HTTP/8080<br/>TLS 1.2+ (DestinationRule SIMPLE)<br/>Authorized by Authorino"| MaaSAPI

    %% Gateway → Model
    Gateway -->|"Per-model port<br/>After auth + rate limit<br/>X-MaaS headers injected"| ModelPod

    %% Application → External Services
    MaaSAPI -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>TLS<br/>Password (maas-db-config)"| PostgreSQL
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token"| K8sAPI
    Controller -.->|"HTTP/8080<br/>metrics"| Prometheus

